summary:
A creative Engineer, passionate and enthusiastic about the way we people improved and changed our lives with technology. 
Industry experience in Power Plant Operation, Process Drying and Paper Production. Experience in Project Management - large Biomass Boiler Installation.
Played Tennis on professional level.
